Reporting Bugs

 If you have recovered a bug in Citrus, please send us a description to <<dev@citrusframwork.org>>. 
 We listen very carefully for bugs and work hard on the issues you presented to us.
 
 We would also be happy for any help you can give us. In case you want to fix a bug yourself 
 see {{{contributing.html}how to contribute code changes}}.